{"id":584219,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/女权行动派很好吃-质问千聊ceo：直播平台为何反女/","date":"2018-05-07T06:37:54Z","modified":"2018-05-07T06:37:54Z","title":"女权行动派很好吃 | 质问千聊CEO：直播平台为何反女权？","content":"<p>这世道账号动不动就被炸，敏感词也越来越多，言论空间不断紧缩，现在连直播平台都开始屏蔽“女木又”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/10268eec-e183-408e-8920-cb0b52195aa2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-584220\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/10268eec-e183-408e-8920-cb0b52195aa2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"342\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/10268eec-e183-408e-8920-cb0b52195aa2.png 342w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/10268eec-e183-408e-8920-cb0b52195aa2-300x284.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 342px) 100vw, 342px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以上图为例，“反对”、“性骚扰”已均被设为敏感词，那么今天被屏蔽的是“女权”，明天被屏蔽的又会是什么呢？</p>\n<p>这种形式下，若是不发声，言论空间将越来越小。沉默，就无异于群体自愿消亡。</p>\n<p>下图为10位女权主义者共同写给千聊 CEO的公开联名信，内容下方附有联署二维码，留下你的名字和留言，女权主义者们联合起来要发声！</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/d3ff9085-af75-420f-9bc1-848e9dcc40ee.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-584221\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/d3ff9085-af75-420f-9bc1-848e9dcc40ee.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"635\" height=\"3301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/d3ff9085-af75-420f-9bc1-848e9dcc40ee.jpg 635w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/d3ff9085-af75-420f-9bc1-848e9dcc40ee-197x1024.jpg 197w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[34557,14699,32914,34556,29781,9283,34558]}